2)	Give a string that may contain letter digit space etc. extract all digit character, read them as number (single digits) then computer and output:(1) their sum (2) their average (3) Their maximum digit (4) there minimum digit.  if no digit prints an appropriate message.
Ans:
     text = input("Enter a string: ")
digits = []
for ch in text:
    if ch.isdigit():
        digits.append(int(ch))
if len(digits) == 0:
    print("No digits found")
else:
    total = sum(digits)
